properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Great Egg Inlet to Cape May NJ out 20 nm; Coastal waters from Little Egg Inlet to Great Egg Inlet NJ out 20 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 17 at 2:48PM EST until February 18 at 9:00PM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...South winds 10 to 15 kt with gusts up to 20 kt and seas
4 to 6 feet expected.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Little Egg Inlet to Cape May NJ out
20 nm.

* WHEN...From 9 AM to 9 PM EST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM TO 9 PM EST TUESDAY
